"I was scared for my life. They accused me of trespassing and they started beating me up. junkWillem Oosthuizen and Theo Martins Jackson appeared in the Middelburg Magistrate's Court on Wednesday after a video of them forcing 27-year-old Mlotshwa into a coffin after assaulting him became public.The video was filmed near JM de Beer Boerdery next to the Komati Power Station close to Middelburg in Mpumalanga.In the 20-second clip the men can be heard forcing Mlotshwa into coffin and threatening to douse him with petrol. When Mlotshwa resisted his captors then threatened to put a snake in the casket.They face charges of assault with the intent to cause grievous bodily harm.